thanks, Works fine

Right -click ACMBOOT.EXE
>Properties
>>Compatability Tab
>>>Run this program in compatability mode for:
>>>>Windows NT 4.0
>>>Disable visual themes
>>>Disable Desktop composition
>>>Disable display scaling on high DPI settings
>>>Run this program as an admin
>>OK
Run ACMBOOT.EXE using the key from visual_basic_6.txt
On error, exit this exe.
Right click SETUP.EXE
>Properties
>>Compatability Tab
>>>Run this program in compatability mode for:
>>>>Windows NT 4.0
>>>Disable visual themes
>>>Disable Desktop composition
>>>Disable display scaling on high DPI settings
>>>Run this program as an admin
>>OK
Run SETUP.EXE
Do not let this program install anything other than VB6, including Install Wizard.
Do not check the box for MSDN.
